* Install portaudio devel headers and https://github.com/arodland/IO-Async-PortAudio
* Install ATLAS static libraries (libatlas-base-dev on Debian)
* git submodule init
* git submodule update --recursive
* perl Build.PL
* ./Build
* perl -Iblib/lib -Iblib/arch eg/hello-snowboy.pl
* Say "snowboy" into the mic.
